#
# Before big changes:
#   make backup  - Create backup
#
# If something goes wrong:
#   make restart - Full restart
#   make stop    - Emergency stop
#   make start   - Start again
#
# Maintenance:
#   make cleanup - Free disk space
#   make stats   - Check resources
